{"tid":1141872,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[童年web game] 發現咗個15秒版GYAGOO","createTime":"2019-05-06T18:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T03:48:14.000Z","uid":63682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0818abe81fd812817019d6c71bd4ff456cc7bc9c","tid":1141872,"uid":63682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"依家網上得返30秒版嘅vagoo 60秒版嘅gyagoo (中文版) 同埋15秒版嘅gyagoo (日文版)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://myhome.ryuhoku.jp/gyagoo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyhome.ryuhoku.jp%2Fgyagoo%2F&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=e74b032d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://myhome.ryuhoku.jp/gyagoo/</a><br />\n上面條link係15版GYAGOO嘅網，強烈推薦大家玩依個。同ZYAGOO差唔多，但無咗黃金山同埋食饅頭升能力，但相對地有其他方法去升能力同刷錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nilhk.cstudy.com/vagoo/index.cgi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnilhk.cstudy.com%2Fvagoo%2Findex.cgi&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=2cebc60d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nilhk.cstudy.com/vagoo/index.cgi</a><br />\n上面果個係30秒嘅vagoo，係最原始版。打到試鍊之山果隻boss就打爆機，相對上升Lv / 推圖會比gyagoo慢好多<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gyagoo.oldtu.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgyagoo.oldtu.com%2F&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=efc0357d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gyagoo.oldtu.com/</a><br />\n上面依個係60秒版嘅gyagoo，雖然係中文版，但每次打怪都要等60秒同埋升得仲慢過15秒版，不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.egamex.net/thread-5544-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.egamex.net%2Fthread-5544-1-1.html&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=026e1236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.egamex.net/thread-5544-1-1.html</a><br />\n上面條link講咗GYAGOO嘅攻略，大家有興趣可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懶人包: <br />\n頭30Lv 慢慢刷怪同埋轉職轉做「戰士」。30Lv後就可以去金字塔/森林/王城/試鍊火山打D勁裝，之後就轉職轉做「侍」。打到70Lv左右就可以去打boss。對之後果d攻略有興趣就自己睇埋佢啦<br />\n<br />\n以下係其他資料:<br />\nGYAGOO基本資料:<a href=\"https://egamex.net/thread-6237-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fegamex.net%2Fthread-6237-1-1.html&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=874818a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://egamex.net/thread-6237-1-1.html</a><br />\nGYAGOO裝備: <a href=\"https://egamex.net/thread-7344-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fegamex.net%2Fthread-7344-1-1.html&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=2a8ad431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://egamex.net/thread-7344-1-1.html</a><br />\nGYAGOO地圖:<a href=\"https://egamex.net/thread-4978-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fegamex.net%2Fthread-4978-1-1.html&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=72303357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://egamex.net/thread-4978-1-1.html</a><br />\nGYAGOO部份整合資料:<a href=\"http://alyro.myweb.hinet.net/gyagoo.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Falyro.myweb.hinet.net%2Fgyagoo.htm&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=802e52d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://alyro.myweb.hinet.net/gyagoo.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，如果大家用iPhone / iPad 玩嘅話，可能會見到亂碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以要將部iPhone個語言轉去日文先會睇到d字。但用PC玩就應該無問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb9cb9a2eb0c78f14ad0321bf5c80041128c1c0","tid":1141872,"uid":63682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7b64a0d8f694b5d5457b7923258887ae0ce919","tid":1141872,"uid":63682,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20