>"},{"pid":"8da03fdcce0b718b0205fcb085a2f0efe466691f","tid":1141872,"uid":167584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"有無巴打有玩過一隻叫做 諸神的黃昏 既文字game?<br />\n又係不斷轉職轉到每個職業都做過就可以做英雄<br />\n我當年同Ｄ台仔一齊玩玩得好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外仲有一隻係儲齊１２星座既寶石就可以加能力值，又係好好玩。"},{"pid":"1344de2059dbafd106faed90e0a0a538bb877369","tid":1141872,"uid":78381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"樓主有無咩心得攻略分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小學成日玩  一直想玩番"},{"pid":"1e9e7a64edf6d251eff9c0f21299b61550aa5133","tid":1141872,"uid":63682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1344de2059dbafd106faed90e0a0a538bb877369","tid":1141872,"uid":78381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"樓主有無咩心得攻略分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小學成日玩  一直想玩番"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:50:59.000Z","msg":"用錢狂升AC 之後儲錢轉生 不停loop<br />\n<br />\n利申 已棄驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45070d19f8e7e3d398495312f493d4c746c35946","tid":1141872,"uid":79245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8da03fdcce0b718b0205fcb085a2f0efe466691f","tid":1141872,"uid":167584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"有無巴打有玩過一隻叫做 諸神的黃昏 既文字game?<br />\n又係不斷轉職轉到每個職業都做過就可以做英雄<br />\n我當年同Ｄ台仔一齊玩玩得好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外仲有一隻係儲齊１２星座既寶石就可以加能力值，又係好好玩。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T03:48:14.000Z","msg":"識貨  sos2  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}